## System Data Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Dashboard
    participant Tracker
    participant Logger
    participant Verifier
    participant Rollback
    participant Firebase
    participant Submodules
    
    Note over User,Submodules: Migration Tracking System Data Flow
    
    %% Initialization Phase
    User->>Tracker: Initialize System
    Tracker->>Firebase: Scan Functions
    Firebase-->>Tracker: Function Inventory
    Tracker->>Logger: Log Discovery
    Tracker-->>User: Inventory Complete
    
    %% Migration Planning Phase
    User->>Dashboard: View Status
    Dashboard->>Tracker: Get Function Status
    Tracker-->>Dashboard: Status Data
    Dashboard-->>User: Display Dashboard
    
    User->>Tracker: Get Ready Functions
    Tracker->>Tracker: Calculate Readiness Scores
    Tracker-->>User: Ready Function List
    
    %% Migration Execution Phase
    User->>Rollback: Create Backup
    Rollback->>Firebase: Backup Function
    Rollback->>Logger: Log Backup
    Rollback-->>User: Backup Created
    
    User->>Tracker: Update Status (In Progress)
    Tracker->>Logger: Log Status Change
    Tracker->>Dashboard: Notify Status Change
    
    %% Function Migration (External Process)
    Note over Firebase,Submodules: Function Migrated to Submodule
    
    %% Verification Phase
    User->>Verifier: Verify Migration
    Verifier->>Submodules: Run Tests
    Submodules-->>Verifier: Test Results
    Verifier->>Logger: Log Verification
    
    alt Verification Successful
        Verifier-->>User: Verification Passed
        User->>Tracker: Update Status (Verified)
    else Verification Failed
        Verifier-->>User: Verification Failed
        User->>Rollback: Execute Rollback
        Rollback->>Submodules: Restore from Backup
        Rollback->>Logger: Log Rollback
        Rollback-->>User: Rollback Complete
    end
    
    %% Monitoring Phase
    loop Continuous Monitoring
        Dashboard->>Tracker: Get Status Updates
        Tracker-->>Dashboard: Current Status
        Dashboard->>Logger: Get Recent Logs
        Logger-->>Dashboard: Log Entries
    end
```

